divs: Sighting Detailsi was walking outside my house to the driveway and it was around 11- 12 at night when i heard this really loud hovering noise. i wasn't paying much attention then i walked a little and looked up and saw a really large ring in the sky, like a doughnut like if you turned a flashlight upside down and put a sticker in the middle. when i looked up the noise stopped and once i realized it was there it disappeared. after the experience i was very unnerved and experienced paranoia like someone was watching me, or something.
